OL,7,FBy the end of this week, the
OL,8,Fgovernment is likely to be closing in
OL,9,Fon a controversial decision on how to
OL,10,Fdeal with severe overcrowding in
OL,11,Fprisons.
OL,13,FThe most probable option taken by the
OL,14,Fnew Justice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,15,Fis to change the automatic release
OL,16,Fpoint on standard determinate
OL,17,Fsentences from 50% of the sentence to
OL,18,F40%.
