OL,7,FThose sentences do not cover the most
OL,8,Fserious cases like murder and rape,
OL,9,Fbut they do include other serious
OL,10,Fcrimes.
OL,12,FIt is my understanding that Ms Mahmood
OL,13,Fis likely to exclude two categories if
OL,14,Fshe goes ahead with the reform: sex
OL,15,Fcrimes and serious violence.
