OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FThat would still leave a situation in
OL,8,Fwhich those convinced of burglary
OL,9,Fcould be released earlier. But
OL,10,FMinistry of Justice (MoJ) sources
OL,11,Fstress the release is on licence and
OL,12,Fthat people can be returned to jail if
OL,13,Fthey break the conditions of their
OL,14,Frelease.
OL,16,FI'm told previous Conservative Justice
OL,17,FSecretary Alex Chalk was considering
OL,18,Fthe same change with exclusions.
