OL,7,FBut even this controversial decision
OL,8,Fwould only delay the prison crisis for
OL,9,F18 months.
OL,11,FSources say the plans needed to go
OL,12,Falongside an overhaul in sentencing
OL,13,Fthat would see fewer people sent to
OL,14,Fjail for short sentences.
OL,16,FMr Chalk was also keen to take action
OL,17,Fin this area, with officials arguing
OL,18,Fthat a 55% reoffending rate with a
OL,19,Fshort sentence is cut to 24% if the
OL,20,Fsentence is suspended.
