OL,7,FJames Timpson, who has been appointed
OL,8,Fas a prisons minister, has long argued
OL,9,Fthat too many people are jailed.
OL,11,FTackling short sentences would be one
OL,12,Fway to lift pressure on jail. But
OL,13,Fanother would be to tackle court
OL,14,Fdelays, as a spike in the number of
OL,15,Fpeople on remand and in custody is a
OL,16,Fmajor driver overcrowding.
